  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >So, you're plunging into a world where our bad-ass, ghost-busting squad (also known as S.P.A.T.) slays night creeps that will probably give you nightmares. You’ll need to be sharp and fast to outsmart and defeat these freaky creatures. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this game, it's clear as day: we tackle eerie critters like Bigfoot, Twilight wannabes (werewolves), mythical cannibals (wendigos), broomstick-riders (witches), and a whole festival of horror. Get ready for some gnarly weapon customization, a chilling vibe, some random scares, and a pinch of naughty humor that will tickle your funny bone. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Customizable Arsenal</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1565660/extras/3a0b4c7c07ccc30a1d4e4ad1dc78fcaf.poster.avif?t=1746293454\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1565660/extras/3a0b4c7c07ccc30a1d4e4ad1dc78fcaf.webm?t=1746293454\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1565660/extras/3a0b4c7c07ccc30a1d4e4ad1dc78fcaf.mp4?t=1746293454\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gear up with a ton of guns and cool gadgets. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Boost up those weapons as per your gaming style and also try messing around with spooky attachments to ace the fight against these monsters. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Spooky Storytime</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1565660/extras/2b136be7bf9b67c6e38693ee6450ea3d.poster.avif?t=1746293454\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1565660/extras/2b136be7bf9b67c6e38693ee6450ea3d.webm?t=1746293454\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1565660/extras/2b136be7bf9b67c6e38693ee6450ea3d.mp4?t=1746293454\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready to untangle creepy local legends and confront horrific nightmares from urban myths. Even if you're armed to your teeth, can you handle the chills going down your spine? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Watch out for four monster-bosses hiding in the dark and a big nasty mob of eerie beasts!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Brutal Buddy Action</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1565660/extras/6a7f307ed90fd243dd5985ed7bf95beb.poster.avif?t=1746293454\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1565660/extras/6a7f307ed90fd243dd5985ed7bf95beb.webm?t=1746293454\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1565660/extras/6a7f307ed90fd243dd5985ed7bf95beb.mp4?t=1746293454\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Raise hell with your squad of an elite team in our adrenaline-spiking co-op mode! Strategize your attacks, cover for each other, and rain down a symphony of destruction on those freaky monsters. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Remember, in SPAT's universe, working together is your golden ticket to survival - and there's nothing like beating down horror movie rejects with your friends!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Black Comedy & Chills</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1565660/extras/d104f4f53be759ee64ea6df9c783c13c.poster.avif?t=1746293454\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1565660/extras/d104f4f53be759ee64ea6df9c783c13c.webm?t=1746293454\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1565660/extras/d104f4f53be759ee64ea6df9c783c13c.mp4?t=1746293454\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prepare for a nerve-racking journey loaded with dark humor and the odd jump-scare. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready to laugh at the madness, but remember, it's a thin line between giggles and screams in this unsettling world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >So why wait? Join Those Who are Already Fighting Monsters!</h2>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >So, you're plunging into a world where our bad-ass, ghost-busting squad (also known as S.P.A.T.) slays night creeps that will probably give you nightmares. You’ll need to be sharp and fast to outsmart and defeat these freaky creatures. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this game, it's clear as day: we tackle eerie critters like Bigfoot, Twilight wannabes (werewolves), mythical cannibals (wendigos), broomstick-riders (witches), and a whole festival of horror. Get ready for some gnarly weapon customization, a chilling vibe, some random scares, and a pinch of naughty humor that will tickle your funny bone. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Customizable Arsenal</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1565660/extras/3a0b4c7c07ccc30a1d4e4ad1dc78fcaf.poster.avif?t=1746293454\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1565660/extras/3a0b4c7c07ccc30a1d4e4ad1dc78fcaf.webm?t=1746293454\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1565660/extras/3a0b4c7c07ccc30a1d4e4ad1dc78fcaf.mp4?t=1746293454\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gear up with a ton of guns and cool gadgets. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Boost up those weapons as per your gaming style and also try messing around with spooky attachments to ace the fight against these monsters. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Spooky Storytime</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop pl