al - and there's nothing like beating down horror movie rejects with your friends!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Black Comedy & Chills</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1565660/extras/d104f4f53be759ee64ea6df9c783c13c.poster.avif?t=1746293454\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1565660/extras/d104f4f53be759ee64ea6df9c783c13c.webm?t=1746293454\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1565660/extras/d104f4f53be759ee64ea6df9c783c13c.mp4?t=1746293454\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prepare for a nerve-racking journey loaded with dark humor and the odd jump-scare. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready to laugh at the madness, but remember, it's a thin line between giggles and screams in this unsettling world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >So why wait? Join Those Who are Already Fighting Monsters!</h2>",
